      <title>西班牙交易裁决临近，BBVA 与萨瓦德尔银行在竞争问题上发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/bbva-sabadell-clash-on-competition-as-spain-deal-verdict-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在西班牙竞争管理机构即将作出裁决的几周前，西班牙对外银行 (BBVA SA) 和萨瓦德尔银行 (Banco Sabadell SA) 就其拟议收购这家小型银行是否会损害西班牙的银行服务供应发生争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/bbva-sabadell-clash-on-competition-as-spain-deal-verdict-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 10:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Teva 因贬低竞争对手被欧盟罚款 4.63 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/teva-hit-with-463-million-eu-fine-for-talking-down-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梯瓦制药工业有限公司 (Teva Pharmaceutical Industries Ltd.) 因不公平地贬低多发性硬化症药物的竞争对手而阻碍公平竞争，被欧盟反垄断监管机构罚款近 4.63 亿欧元（5.03 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/teva-hit-with-463-million-eu-fine-for-talking-down-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 10:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员加大对泰晤士水务公司紧急资金的竞标力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/traders-boost-bids-for-slice-of-thames-water-s-emergency-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债务交易商正在提高泰晤士水务公司试图从债权人那里获得的拟议紧急资金的部分出价，这表明这些条款对投资者具有吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/traders-boost-bids-for-slice-of-thames-water-s-emergency-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 10:33:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
